    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_43217835" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/43217835" />
    <a title="Stephanie Butland" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1847457-stephanie-butland"><img alt="Stephanie Butland" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1515176388p2/1847457.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/43217835?book_show_action=true">Jan 16, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Stephanie Butland" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Stephanie Butland" href="/user/show/1847457-stephanie-butland">Stephanie Butland</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer43217835" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4023183130279824773">This is that rare thing - a book I gave up on. I realised after 100 pages or so that I was actually dreading reading it.... a disappointment, as I loved <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15888.An_Instance_of_the_Fingerpost_A_Novel' title='An Instance of the Fingerpost A Novel by Iain Pears' rel='nofollow noopener'>An Instance of the Fingerpost A Novel</a>by the same author. </span>
  <span id="freeText4023183130279824773" style="display:none">This is that rare thing - a book I gave up on. I realised after 100 pages or so that I was actually dreading reading it.... a disappointment, as I loved <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15888.An_Instance_of_the_Fingerpost_A_Novel" title="An Instance of the Fingerpost A Novel by Iain Pears" rel="nofollow noopener">An Instance of the Fingerpost A Novel</a>by the same author. </span>
