        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3282698560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15007957474920187737">A literary historical fiction that weaves the lives of three men around the classic work, The Dream of Scipio that explores the relevance of the work to three completely different time periods.<br/><br/>Book Club material.</span>

